#             X_ICED [m]:  X-coordinate of the iced surface
#             Y_ICED [m]:  Y-coordinate of the iced surface
#             Z_ICED [m]:  Z-coordinate of the iced surface
#
#                XXmm:  Roughness height used for the case, in mm.
#                       In the zone name, use the format KS_XXmm.
#                       For example, if k_s = 1.5 mm, use KS_1p5mm. 
#                       For Variable roughness, use KS_VAR
#
#    FLOW CONDITIONS:
#                                   AOA: 2.0 deg
#                           Mach Number: 0.4 [-]
#       Mean aerodynamic chord (M.A.C.): 0.801673 [m]
#                       Reynolds Number: 4.2558 million (based on MAC)
